question: Qual é o nome de todos os atores?

api_response.query:
SELECT T1.first_name, T1.last_name
FROM actor AS T1;

question: Quantos filmes foram lançados no ano 2006?
Liste os filmes com classificação 'PG-13' e seus respectivos idiomas.

api_response.query:
SELECT F1.title, L1.name
FROM film AS F1
JOIN language AS L1 ON F1.original_language_id = L1.language_id
WHERE F1.rating = 'PG-13';

question: Qual cliente alugou mais filmes e quantos foram?

api_response.query:
SELECT c.first_name, c.last_name, COUNT(r.rental_id) AS num_rentals
FROM customer AS c
JOIN rental AS r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id
GROUP BY c.customer_id, c.first_name, c.last_name
ORDER BY num_rentals DESC;
